# 09.02 Stage 0 — Foundation

## Overview

Stage 0 defines the foundation phase of cmdOS development.

The purpose of this stage is to establish the technical, architectural, and organizational foundation required to build the AI Execution Operating System.

Before creating advanced Agents or execution systems, cmdOS must first establish:

- Clear architecture
- Development infrastructure
- Core principles
- Engineering standards
- Initial AI foundation

Core principle:

Vision

↓

Architecture

↓

Foundation

↓

Future Development

---

# 1. Stage 0 Purpose

The purpose of Stage 0 is to create the minimum foundation required for future cmdOS evolution.

The main objectives are:

- Define system architecture
- Establish development standards
- Create repository structure
- Build initial AI infrastructure
- Prepare execution framework

---

# 2. Stage 0 Position

Stage 0 is the first step in the cmdOS roadmap.

Roadmap relationship:

Stage 0

↓

MVP

↓

Agent Platform

↓

Execution OS

↓

