# 3. Stage 0 Goals

The main goals of Stage 0:

## Technical Foundation

Create the base architecture for cmdOS.

Includes:

- Kernel concept
- Runtime concept
- Agent architecture
- Capability model
- Plugin architecture

---

## Development Foundation

Create engineering infrastructure.

Includes:

- Repository structure
- Documentation system
- Development workflow
- Testing framework

---

## AI Foundation

Prepare the intelligence layer.

Includes:

- AI model routing
- Context management
- Reasoning architecture
- Initial Agent framework

