# 12. Stage 0 Success Criteria

Stage 0 is successful when:

- Architecture is clearly defined
- Development workflow exists
- Core components have boundaries
- AI foundation is prepared
- MVP development can begin

---

# 13. Stage 0 Limitations

Stage 0 does not focus on:

- Full desktop automation
- Large Agent ecosystem
- Enterprise deployment
- Marketplace scale

These belong to later stages.

