# Summary

Stage 0 creates the foundation of cmdOS.

It establishes:

- Architecture
- Engineering standards
- AI foundation
- Development environment
- Security principles

This stage transforms cmdOS from a vision into a buildable system.

Stage 0 is the foundation that enables the future AI Execution Operating System.
